      "updated": 1716192000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\u2022 kicktipp.py, strategies.py \u2014 vendored\n  (kopiert aus kicktipp-mcp, kein Sync)\n\u2022 main.py \u2014 Bot (LLM-Strategie)\n\u2022 tracking.py / odds_history.py /\n  ranking_history.py \u2014 Scoring & Historie\n\u2022 dashboard_data.py \u2014 geteilte Payload-Logik\n\u2022 dashboard.py \u2014 lokaler Server (voller Payload)\n\u2022 api/data.py \u2014 Vercel Function (nur Community)\n\u2022 web/dashboard.html \u2014 UI (lokal + gehostet)\n\u2022 .github/workflows/kicktipp-bot.yml \u2014 Cron",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2022 kicktipp.py, strategies.py \u2014 vendored\n  (kopiert aus kicktipp-mcp, kein Sync)\n\u2022 main.py \u2014 Bot (LLM-Strategie)\n\u2022 tracking.py / odds_history.py /\n  ranking_history.py \u2014 Scoring & Historie\n\u2022 dashboard_data.py \u2014 geteilte Payload-Logik\n\u2022 dashboard.py \u2014 lokaler Server (voller Payload)\n\u2022 api/data.py \u2014 Vercel Function (nur Community)\n\u2022 web/dashboard.html \u2014 UI (lokal + gehostet)\n\u2022 .github/workflows/kicktipp-bot.yml \u2014 Cron",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
